  <sect3 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to GNOME Nibbles</title>

    <para>
      <application>gnome-nibbles</application> is a Snake game for 
      <application>GNOME</application>. 
      The aim of the game is to swallow as many objects as you can 
      while avoiding maze walls and other worms.
    </para>

    &lfs76_checked;

